The application is created in order to take
free time and programming brings some pleasure.

Dependences:
app-shells/bash
x11-misc/gtkdialog
app-misc/screen

Optional dependences:
gnome-extra/zenity
app-admin/sudo (or launch as root)

Install:
cd /some_dir
tar xvf /path/to/emerzo.tar.gz ./

Launch:
/some_dir/emerzo.sh

You can also rename the script as needed.
